WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.236 --> 00:00:04.037
- OKAY,
LET'S GET THIS THING GOING.

00:00:04.137 --> 00:00:07.140
EVERYBODY TAKE A SEAT.

00:00:07.241 --> 00:00:10.210
WE GOT TO HAVE
MORE MEETINGS, HOMES,

00:00:10.310 --> 00:00:12.980
'CAUSE I'M TELLING YOU, MAN,
WE GOT TO GET ORGANIZED.

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:14.648
[sighs]

00:00:14.748 --> 00:00:19.152
[police sirens in the distance]

00:00:25.425 --> 00:00:28.128
CARLITO AIN'T GOT A SEAT, MAN.
SOMEONE GET HIM A CHAIR.

00:00:28.228 --> 00:00:29.563
- NO, I'M COOL.

00:00:29.663 --> 00:00:32.332
- NO, DUDE, GET HIM A CHAIR,
HOMES.

00:00:35.402 --> 00:00:37.137
- I'M GONNA SIT GANGSTER.

00:00:37.237 --> 00:00:39.873
- BUT, CARLITO, IT DOESN'T LOOK
LIKE IT'S COMFORTABLE, MAN.

00:00:39.973 --> 00:00:42.476
WHY DON'T YOU
JUST SIT IN THE CHAIR?

00:00:42.576 --> 00:00:44.711
- I NEVER SIT
IN NO CHAIR, <i>ESE.</i>

00:00:44.811 --> 00:00:46.580
MM-MMM.

00:00:46.680 --> 00:00:50.350
YOU NEVER, EVER GON' CATCH ME
SITTING IN NO CHAIRS.

00:00:50.450 --> 00:00:52.252
- HEY, <i>ESE,</i> YOU KNOW THAT
THAT'S LOCO, RIGHT?

00:00:52.352 --> 00:00:53.854
- NO, MAN.
[scoffs]

00:00:53.954 --> 00:00:55.088
- IT'S COOL, CARLITO.

00:00:55.189 --> 00:00:56.790
NO ONE'S GONNA THINK
YOU'RE SOFT

00:00:56.890 --> 00:00:58.425
IF YOU SIT IN A CHAIR, HOMES.
- YEAH, YEAH.

00:00:58.525 --> 00:00:59.960
- WE'RE ALL SITTING IN CHAIRS.
- RIGHT.

00:01:00.060 --> 00:01:02.229
- BUNCH OF BITCH-ASS <i>CULEROS.</i>

00:01:02.329 --> 00:01:03.897
- <i>QUE?</i>
- I DON'T HAVE NO TIME

00:01:03.997 --> 00:01:06.500
TO SIT IN NO [bleep] CHAIR.

00:01:08.669 --> 00:01:10.771
- OKAY.

00:01:10.871 --> 00:01:13.407
NOW THAT WE'RE ALL HERE--

00:01:13.507 --> 00:01:14.942
YOU KNOW WHAT?
BUT WHY, THOUGH?

00:01:15.042 --> 00:01:17.845
LIKE, IT DON'T MAKE NO SENSE
FOR YOU TO SET YOURSELF UP

00:01:17.945 --> 00:01:19.413
WITH A RULE LIKE THAT.

00:01:19.513 --> 00:01:22.282
- NO, IT'S, LIKE, LIMITING.
- YEAH, LIMITING.

00:01:22.382 --> 00:01:23.684
- LIMITING.
- I MEAN, SOMETIMES,

00:01:23.784 --> 00:01:25.118
PEOPLE SIT IN CHAIRS.

00:01:25.219 --> 00:01:27.988
- MAN, [bleep] ALL OF YOU GUYS
WITH YOUR BITCH-ASS CHAIRS.

00:01:28.088 --> 00:01:29.790
[wood cracks]

00:01:29.890 --> 00:01:33.393
- THERE.
- [scoffs]

00:01:33.493 --> 00:01:37.097
- OKAY, CARLITO, QUIT PLAYING
AND SIT IN THE CHAIR, <i>PENDEJO.</i>

00:01:37.197 --> 00:01:38.665
- NO.
- CARLITO,

00:01:38.765 --> 00:01:41.768
WE HAVE TO HAVE THIS MEETING
NOW, <i>ESE.</i> GET UP!

00:01:41.869 --> 00:01:43.370
- I'M GOOD RIGHT HERE, MAN.

00:01:43.470 --> 00:01:45.105
- YOU KNOW--
- I'M CHILLING.

00:01:45.205 --> 00:01:47.374
GO AHEAD WITH YOUR MEETING.

00:01:47.474 --> 00:01:50.377
- OKAY, BUT YOU KNOW
IT'S GOING TO BE WEIRD.

00:01:50.477 --> 00:01:51.745
YOU DON'T CARE
THAT IT'S GOING TO BE WEIRD?

00:01:51.845 --> 00:01:52.880
- WEIRD FOR YOU, MAYBE.

00:01:52.980 --> 00:01:55.249
- HE DOESN'T CARE.
OKAY.

00:01:55.349 --> 00:01:58.485
OKAY, HOMIES,
SO THIS IS WHAT WE HAVE TO DO,

00:01:58.585 --> 00:02:00.153
LIKE, WE GOT TO SELL
MORE DRUGS...

00:02:00.254 --> 00:02:01.522
- [groaning]
- AND WE GOT TO MAKE

00:02:01.622 --> 00:02:02.890
MORE CRIMES HAPPEN.

00:02:02.990 --> 00:02:05.792
ROBERTO, WHERE ARE WE--
- [groaning]

00:02:05.893 --> 00:02:08.028
- CARLITO,
YOU'RE BLEEDING, <i>ESE!</i>

00:02:08.128 --> 00:02:10.697
- [grunts]
WHO CARES, MAN?

00:02:10.797 --> 00:02:14.334
[winces]

00:02:14.434 --> 00:02:16.170
- YO, WHOA!
YOU JUST GOT SHANKED, MAN!

00:02:16.270 --> 00:02:18.539
WE GOT TO PULL THAT OUT!
- LEAVE IT!

00:02:18.639 --> 00:02:21.008
I'M CHILLING, HOMES.

00:02:21.108 --> 00:02:24.411
I DON'T CARE
ABOUT THAT STUPID SHANK.

00:02:24.511 --> 00:02:26.780
[groaning]

00:02:26.880 --> 00:02:27.981
[exhales]

00:02:28.081 --> 00:02:29.783
- CARLITO.

00:02:29.883 --> 00:02:32.319
CARLITO, WAKE UP, MAN!

00:02:32.419 --> 00:02:35.689
[radio chatter]

00:02:35.789 --> 00:02:37.124
- HEY,
DON'T EVEN BOTHER, <i>ESE.</i>

00:02:37.224 --> 00:02:38.559
- WHAT?
[screams]

00:02:38.659 --> 00:02:40.127
OH, <i>DIOS MIO!</i>

00:02:40.227 --> 00:02:42.996
- I DON'T NEED
THOSE DEFIBRILLATORS.

00:02:43.096 --> 00:02:45.199
I DON'T EVEN WANT TO COME BACK
TO LIFE, HOMES.

00:02:45.299 --> 00:02:48.702
- CARLITO,
GO BACK INTO YOUR BODY.

00:02:48.802 --> 00:02:51.605
- MY BODY'S STUPID, HOMES.
- WHAT?

00:02:51.705 --> 00:02:54.107
- I'M FINE RIGHT HERE
ON THE SPIRIT PLANE.

00:02:54.208 --> 00:02:56.510
LIFE IS FOR PUSSIES.

00:02:56.610 --> 00:03:00.614
[heavenly singing]

00:03:00.714 --> 00:03:04.685
- CARLITO.
CARLITO, GO TO THE LIGHT.

00:03:04.785 --> 00:03:06.353
- NAH, I'M GOOD, MAN.

00:03:06.453 --> 00:03:08.021
- CARLITO,
THAT'S HEAVEN, MAN.

00:03:08.121 --> 00:03:09.723
- I DON'T NEED TO GO
TO HEAVEN, HOMES.

00:03:09.823 --> 00:03:10.591
HEAVEN IS FOR PUSSIES.
- OH, BOY.

